Package projectfour

Class NYPizzaController

java.lang.Object
projectfour.NYPizzaController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class NYPizzaController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The NYPizzaController is a controller for the New York pizza window. This class will create pizza orders of New York style pizzas and add to the current order.
Author:
Jaspreet Kaur, Kerimcan Baba
